title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 175-1.11 - Judicial review
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 175-1.11 - Judicial review

State Regulations

In the letter transmitting the decision, the hearing
officer shall advise the parties of the availability of judicial review, pursuant to article 78 of the Civil Practice Law and Rules. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9
§§
175-1.11

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
